This projects aims at creating an emacs frontend to Eclim, see http://eclim.sourceforge.net. With the help of ecilm we can provide emacs-users with a tight eclipse integration. The ultimate goal of the project is to simplify java development with emacs and bring the best features from eclipse to emacs.

